OL,3,CFirefighters rescue six people,
OL,4,Cincluding a child, from Woolwich blaze
OL,6,FSix people were rescued by
OL,7,Ffirefighters after a blaze broke out
OL,8,Fat a three-storey building in south-
OL,9,Feast London.
OL,11,FFive adults and a child were taken to
OL,12,Fhospital to be treated for smoke
OL,13,Finhalation after crews responded to
OL,14,Fthe fire on Edge Hill, Woolwich, at
OL,15,F1.35am on Thursday, the London Fire
OL,16,FBrigade (LFB) confirmed.
OL,18,FSome 60 firefighters tackled the
OL,19,Fblaze, where two cars, a caravan,
OL,20,Fgarages and a number flats were
OL,21,Faffected.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
