OL,3,CFirefighters rescue six people,
OL,4,Cincluding a child, from Woolwich blaze
OL,6,FThe LFB said multiple flats were
OL,7,Fdamaged due to the heat of the fire,
OL,8,Fwhile around three garages and all of
OL,9,Fthe vehicles were completely destroyed.
OL,11,FAround 10 people were evacuated from
OL,12,Fthe building in total.
OL,14,FThe blaze was brought under control at
OL,15,F3.59am, with the cause of the fire
OL,16,Funder investigation.
OL,18,FCrews from Plumstead, East Greenwich,
OL,19,FEltham and surrounding fire stations
OL,20,Fresponded to the scene.
